00:31:49.310 --> 00:31:49.920
kung

00:31:51.240 --> 00:31:52.240
Maaari niyang ipadala si Gu Pingyuan

00:31:52.240 --> 00:31:53.550
bumalik sa Ninguta

00:31:55.110 --> 00:31:57.000
at ikakadena siya roon na parang aso

00:31:58.590 --> 00:31:59.920
sa natitirang bahagi ng kanyang buhay,

00:32:03.400 --> 00:32:05.130
